{"title":"蒋区雇工谣","authors":["孔庄潘　佐民权"],"dates":[{"year":1947,"month":7,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒋区雇工谣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"熬活，熬活，誓死不给地主熬活。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在的地主比过去更涩的多。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死气麦茬短把杓，想吃稠的＠不着。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要水烟一摄摄，要火香一撮撮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要钱去胡推胡躲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要的紧了，给两个抽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（孔庄潘、佐民权）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}